"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月10日消息，Ripple执行主席兼联合创始人Chris Larsen公布了他让比特币矿工摆脱工作量证明（PoW）的计划，称他们应该将其视为“对他们长寿的积极影响”。他认为，这将会极大提振上市矿业公司的股价，因为任何新的准则提案几乎肯定都必须包括有利可图的激励措施才能获得他们的支持。\",\"timestamp\":1639112924,\"title\":\"Ripple创始人Chris Larsen说服比特币矿工采用股权证明的回报计划\"},\"digest\":\"DrUL6Z981_qJ1APB7hkyKfUfV7j3SXoq3RrEjjmcw-4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x4eac525d5FBF54cd99Fd1593949714Ad30D66B74\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"264xYlOJrQ4e-x_SqRFeoeyYtEAkEYCd5Q0YPmjLD20\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xhpYF09LCZcpWgbeKepyQ1mPb4GPt1CAwjbOKbbp2rc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ReNlo7Fk71W9q77QJO8doRid--fyElDTV7eMJ15PZ2xlDr92XUG1exlybJLDTIOlsDtfhgL64uZ1fZeLNWQMFQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xbe84ab35cdfa4a21a3793204fbd9224792b82debfbeccae8aecdb63d776b70f37f4dcc042d41592594eff7ead5c22813b27a825742aa7e4ad141be901bcb46711b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"264xYlOJrQ4e-x_SqRFeoeyYtEAkEYCd5Q0YPmjLD20\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xhpYF09LCZcpWgbeKepyQ1mPb4GPt1CAwjbOKbbp2rc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"DrUL6Z981_qJ1APB7hkyKfUfV7j3SXoq3RrEjjmcw-4\"}"